                            Plot No. 326, OUAT Agriculture Farm Road, Baramunda, Bhubaneswar, Odisha, PIN-751003<br>
                            Phone: 91-674-2354125<br>
                            Email: apicol96@yahoo.com
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <ul class="list-unstyled text-white footer-social list-inline">
                            <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="#"><i class="mdi mdi-facebook facebook"></i></a></li>
